<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') %>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="app-info-title text-center mb-4">Chatbot-Based Ticket System</h1>

        <div class="app-info-content">  
            <p>
                Welcome to the Chatbot-Based Ticket System! This system allows users to easily book tickets for various museums 
                by interacting with an AI-powered chatbot. The chatbot will guide you through the process of selecting a museum, 
                entering your details, and generating a ticket.
            </p>

            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Interactive chatbot for seamless ticket booking.</li>
                <li>View museum details including name, location, ticket price, and visiting hours.</li>
                <li>Select the number of members and visit date through the chatbot.</li>
                <li>Instant ticket generation with QR codes for entry and exit.</li>
                <li>Real-time integration with museum databases.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>How to Use the System</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Start a conversation with the chatbot by clicking the chatbot icon on the homepage.</li>
                <li>Follow the chatbot's prompts to select a museum and enter your booking details.</li>
                <li>Once all information is provided, the chatbot will generate your ticket.</li>
                <li>You'll receive a ticket with unique QR codes for both entry and exit to the museum.</li>
            </ol>

            <h3>System Requirements</h3>
            <p>This system works on modern browsers such as Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, and Microsoft Edge. A stable internet connection is required for booking tickets.</p>

            <h3>Contact Information</h3>
            <p>If you have any issues or questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@chatbotticketsystem.com">support@chatbotticketsystem.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-dark">Go to Homepage</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
